{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those old army Jeeps are kind of low to the ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember looking up at this gray, April sky, and it just disappeared in a forest of claws.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean claws, like a Hitchcock movie coming at you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they could not control themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember thinking, they can't-- like a stone falling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They can't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the screaming was a very high-pitched quality, like sea birds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later-- it was from the starvation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The nasal tissues were wasted, the pharynxes were wasted, and it came out with a high-pitched, ahh!",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nasal screams.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I thought, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These people are out of control, they'll tear us to pieces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] the spooky thing, the sensation I can remember as I sit here this afternoon-- they clutched, and the hardest clutch of hundreds of these people-- the hardest, frenzied clutch they could make felt like feathers brushing your face.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like cotton-wool, I remember thinking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was ghostly, like a bunch of ghosts running their hands over you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were clutching as hard as they could clutch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They could not re-- stop themselves when they saw that food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This went on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, there was a little Russian boy, a teenager, who was not as starved as the rest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He helped us get things kind of organized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The poor people could not control themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we kept tearing the loaves of bread in half and giving one to each person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kept cramming it in their mouths, crying and crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a long time to get things in some kind of-- but they were used to standing in lines, and order, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we saw that everybody got some bread in that particular-- until ours was used up.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
